✅ Flight Booking — Complete (Use Case 2)
Architecture & Ports
Eureka (8761) → auth-service (8081) → user-service (8082)
             → flight-service (8083) → booking-service (8084) → payment-service (8085)
             → api-gateway (8080)

Booking Workflow (End-to-End)
Step 1  POST /auth/login              → Get JWT token
        ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Step 2  GET  /flights/search          → Find available flight (get flightId)
        ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Step 3  POST /bookings                → Create booking with passenger details
        Body: { flightId, passengers: [{firstName, lastName, email, phone, age, gender}] }
        ← Returns: bookingReference (BKG-XXXXXXXX), assigned seats, status=PENDING_PAYMENT
        ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Step 4  POST /payments/initiate       → Process payment
        Body: { bookingId, bookingReference, paymentMethod: UPI|CREDIT_CARD|DEBIT_CARD|NET_BANKING }
        ← Returns: paymentReference (PAY-XXXXXXXX), transactionId, status=SUCCESS/FAILED
        ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Step 5  [AUTO] payment-service → booking-service (internal PATCH /bookings/internal/confirm)
        ← booking status: PENDING_PAYMENT → CONFIRMED
        ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Step 6  [AUTO] EmailService logs confirmation email with passenger + seat details

API Endpoints
Booking Service (8084)
Method	Path	Auth	Description
GET	/bookings/health	Public	Health check
POST	/bookings	JWT	Step 1 — Create booking
GET	/bookings/my	JWT	My bookings
GET	/bookings/{id}	JWT	Get by ID
GET	/bookings/reference/{ref}	JWT	Get by reference
POST	/bookings/{id}/cancel	JWT	Cancel PENDING booking
GET	/bookings	ADMIN	All bookings
PATCH	/bookings/internal/confirm	X-Service-Key	Payment callback
Payment Service (8085)
Method	Path	Auth	Description
GET	/payments/health	Public	Health check
POST	/payments/initiate	JWT	Step 2 — Process payment
GET	/payments/my	JWT	My payments
GET	/payments/{id}	JWT	Get by ID
GET	/payments/reference/{ref}	JWT	Get by reference
GET	/payments/booking/{bookingId}	JWT	Get by booking
GET	/payments	ADMIN	All payments
Key Design Decisions
Feature	Implementation
Seat assignment	Auto-assigned (1A→50F), tracks taken seats across active bookings
Booking reference	BKG- + 8 random alphanumeric chars, collision-safe recursive check
Payment reference	PAY- + 8 random alphanumeric chars
Transaction ID	TXN- + timestamp (simulated gateway)
Payment success rates	CREDIT_CARD 92%, UPI 90%, DEBIT_CARD 88%, NET_BANKING 82%
Test failure	simulateFailure: true in payload forces payment failure
Inter-service call	@LoadBalanced RestTemplate → http://BOOKING-SERVICE/bookings/internal/confirm
Service key guard	X-Service-Key: poc-internal-svc-key-2026 protects internal endpoint
Email	Mock EmailService logs formatted email (no SMTP dependency)
Swagger UI	http://localhost:8084/swagger-ui.html & http://localhost:8085/swagger-ui.html